    "悦笺": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "悦笺不含任何广告、第三方分析工具或追踪 SDK，整个应用只使用 Apple 提供的系统框架。我们不收集、也不分析你的使用行为。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy contains no ads, third-party analytics, or tracking SDKs — only Apple system frameworks. We neither collect nor analyze your usage behavior."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋不含任何廣告、第三方分析工具或追蹤 SDK，整個應用程式只使用 Apple 提供的系統框架。我們不收集、也不分析你的使用行為。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "悦笺备份": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy Backup"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋備份"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "悦笺已解锁": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy Unlocked"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋已解鎖"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "悦笺账单-%@": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy-Bills-%@"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋帳單-%@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "悦笺通过一次性购买收费。我们的收入与你的数据完全无关，因此没有任何动机去收集或变现它。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Jotsy charges a one-time purchase fee. Our revenue has nothing to do with your data, so there is zero incentive to collect or monetize it."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "悅箋透過一次性購買收費。我們的收入與你的資料完全無關，因此沒有任何動機去收集或變現它。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
