    "我们默认用 5% 作为温和提醒线，你也可以按自己的消费节奏微调。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "We use 5% as a gentle reminder threshold by default. You can adjust it to match your spending habits."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我們預設用 5% 作為溫和提醒線，你也可以按自己的消費節奏微調。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "我的": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Me"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我的"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "所有数据只存在你的本地设备，清空后无法恢复，卸载 app 也是一样。**请先导出一份 CSV 备份**，需要时可以随时再导入回来。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All data is stored only on your device. Once cleared, it cannot be recovered — same as uninstalling the app. **Please export a CSV backup first** — you can re-import it anytime."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "所有資料只存在你的本機裝置，清空後無法恢復，刪除 app 也是一樣。**請先匯出一份 CSV 備份**，需要時可以隨時再匯入回來。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "所有账单数据由 SwiftData 存储在设备本地。悦笺没有服务器，不会将你的账单上传到任何地方。若你开启了 iCloud 备份，这些数据会随 iOS 系统备份一同加密存储——该过程由你的系统设置控制。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All bill data is stored locally on your device via SwiftData. Jotsy has no servers and never uploads your bills anywhere. If you have iCloud backup enabled, data is encrypted alongside your iOS system backup — controlled by your system settings."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "所有帳單資料由 SwiftData 儲存在裝置本機。悅箋沒有伺服器，不會將你的帳單上傳到任何地方。若你開啟了 iCloud 備份，這些資料會隨 iOS 系統備份一同加密儲存——該過程由你的系統設定控制。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
